Add to a Dialog from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report

Select a report, click the summary name of a topic, select some excerpts and click "Create New Dialog", then select "Add to Existing Dialog".
Choose whether to create an intent or add to intent.
If creating an intent, choose intent set and include details.
If adding to intent, select intent set and intent.
Select bot name, version and dialog.
Click Finish.

Note: Selecting an active bot version creates an inactive version.
